1.  Exigenda

     i18n Even  the  tag->action  mapping should be interna-
          tionalized.

     Tags Allow  specification  of  alternate  (on-the-fly?)
          tags;  <img src="IMAGE/PNG" />, etc.  Substitution
          according to mime.

     XML-RPC
          Either replace the builtin-XML-RPC/curl  implemen-
          tation  with a php one, or allow some sort of cus-
          tomization flag. Care to benchmark?

